import React from 'react';
import {Col, Card} from 'react-bootstrap';


<Col xs={12} md={6} lg={3} key={repo.id}>
<Card>
    <Card.Img variant="top" src={repo.img}/>
    <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>{repo.title}</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
            {repo.description}
        </Card.Text>
    </Card.Body>
</Card>
</Col>
